reviewText: A waste of time and money.
Great video about water conservation and what it means to US... the public, also has some awesome cave diving video.
Everyone should take the time to watch this! It's full of great messages about water from passionate people. Highly recommend it!
A terrific film that shows many of our current problems with water resources as well as some good ideas on solutions.
Intelligent, accessible, real. Nothing has been more effective in convincing me that the issue is real and I can do something about it.
